Beautiful - A library to theme awesome3
---------------------------------------

Installation: 

- Symlink or copy beautiful.lua to your awesome local share folder (i.e: /usr/local/share/awesome/lib for Debian GNU/Linux)
- Symllink or copy the 'themes' folder to ~/.config/awesome/

Don't forget to edit the awesome3 theme to set up your own wallpaper manager

How to use Beautiful:

http://article.gmane.org/gmane.comp.window-managers.awesome/2547

Also, read comments in Beautiful.lua to have extra informations.

oxmoz
